uote>考咩時段<br />\n<br />\n我係永考pass 已經揸緊車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考兩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩點真係祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7360c466a2419870b4b37be85d97d716a08ea257","tid":109552,"uid":31796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n考兩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩點真係祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貨車上落貨等入倉<br />\n如果轉出永基路個路口有個仆街泊左係到頂撚住你就慘<br />\n好就好在未到放學時間同過左學校放飯時間"},{"pid":"27cd10168f23d54556b04949508dfbe1a8d65341","tid":109552,"uid":65597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T01:20:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n考兩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩點真係祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貨車上落貨等入倉<br />\n如果轉出永基路個路口有個仆街泊左係到頂撚住你就慘<br />\n好就好在未到放學時間同過左學校放飯時間</blockquote><br />\n我考果陣 咁岩 有架van 係度落貨 , 呢段路真係要慢慢行，記熟d 路線"},{"pid":"9f29eb38ab8763d83d14e17a9a5e7f3e02bca68f","tid":109552,"uid":57314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:25:24.000Z","msg":"來啦來啦，MolaMola, I am scared<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人打下氣"},{"pid":"28926f52ec93348d24f52d2833191b5bc3c47c08","tid":109552,"uid":32186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>來啦來啦，MolaMola, I am scared<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人打下氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過死車記得打燈望鏡做足d<br />\n小路出大路點都停車望一望<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係lihkg同高登見過兩句野對考車有新既睇法:<br />\n1. 唔好以為上3波係為左開得快, 其實2波同3波都可以行40, 但考試就係要上<br />\n<br />\n2. 考車唔係考你揸車有幾勁, 係睇你安全意識, 即使死火都無大不了, 都會pass<br />\n<br />\n我第二次考個陣小路出大路比架小巴遮住,睇唔到有車出, 一見到即係dup車就死火, 之後抱住肥撚硬既心態繼續鳩揸 點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 葵盛圍新路舊路各考一次<br />\n兩次都係153<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}